parent1.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with flaming feathers in the style of surrealism. It is soaring above the rooftops in an ancient city on a stormy day, scattering embers from its wings, amidst an environment of twisting spires and floating lanterns.

offspring.code: A detailed watercolor of a radiant golden phoenix with fiery flaming feathers in the style of surrealism. It is majestically soaring above the crumbling rooftops in an ancient, mystical city on a stormy, overcast day, gracefully scattering glowing embers from its ethereal wings, amidst an environment of twisting, towering spires and shimmering, floating lanterns.
